Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
HybridSpeedup Class HybridSpeedup is a main program that analyzes running time measurements and reports speedup metrics for a hybrid parallel program.
mprun Class mprun is a main program that runs an MPI job on a cluster parallel computer using the Parallel Java job queue.
ncc Class ncc is a main program that computes the Non-Comment Characters (NCC) metric for each Java source file listed on the command line.
ncsl Class ncsl is a main program that computes the Non-Comment Source Lines (NCSL) metric for each Java source file listed on the command line.
PJG Class PJG is a program that displays a Parallel Java Graphics (PJG) image file.
pjrun Class pjrun is a main program that runs a program, other than a Parallel Java (PJ) program, on a cluster parallel computer using the PJ job queue.
Program1Clu Class Program1Clu is the cluster parallel version of the first program illustrating parallel computing.
Program1Seq Class Program1Seq is the sequential version of the first program illustrating parallel computing.
Program1Smp Class Program1Smp is the SMP parallel version of the first program illustrating parallel computing.
Sizeup Class Sizeup is a main program that analyzes running time measurements and reports sizeup metrics for a parallel program.
Speedup Class Speedup is a main program that analyzes running time measurements and reports speedup metrics for a parallel program.
TimeFit Class TimeFit is a main program that analyzes running time measurements and fits them to a running time model for a parallel program.
View Class View is a main program for displaying a Viewable object on the screen.
